TestIsItemTrueForAnyValue
/ if %x% is item — true for every value: a number, a text, a dict, a list.
/ item is the apex of the type lattice; nothing falls outside.
- set %n% = 1
- assert %n% is item
- set %t% = "hi"
- assert %t% is item
- set %d% = {a:1}
- assert %d% is item
- set %l% = [1, 2]
- assert %l% is item
